title: Daughter of the Sun
description:
DAUGHTER OF THE SUN (1962)
Directed by Herschell Gordon Lewis ("Lewis H. Gordon")
Produced by David F. Friedman ("Davis Freeman")

Starring Rusty Allen and Jerry Eden ("Jerry Stallion")

Filmed in black/white and color (for nature camp sequences)

School board in sunny Florida learns that teacher Rusty Allen is a nudist in private life.  How do you think they react?

Torrent includes two short (10 minute) films from the Something Weird DVD "Diary of a Nudist / Naked Venus" -- 1) They Wear No Clothes and 2) Nudist Recruits -- both were made in the 1930s, I believe.

Tech Specs (I mention these because Daughter of the Sun looks a little gnarly, mostly because of its age & the nature of the film stock. It is a VHS dub from the Something Weird VHS of this film.)

Daughter of the Sun -- Captured to PC as an MPG @ 5000 kbps, then converted to MP4 with Nero Recode @ 2.02 mbps -- 29.97 fps

Short films from DVD -- converted to MPG @ 5000 kbps, then converted to MP4 with Nero Recode @ 2.02 mbps -- 23.98 fps
